# Vercel Platform Conventions

Goal: Prevent path/layout disagreements between agents.

- Default runtime `nodejs`
- Edge only when latency-critical and ADR says so
- Use Vercel Cron for background jobs; jobs must be idempotent + observable
- Use Vercel Observability by default; Sentry optional add-on
- Parallel agent worktrees are a Cursor 2.x feature relying on git worktrees
- Feature flags via `flags` package (not `@vercel/flags`)
- Cron jobs in `/app/api/cron/**/route.ts`
- Environment variables via Vercel dashboard or `.env.local`
